# Kanban Backend API

This is the backend part of a Kanban board application built with Django and Django REST Framework.  
It offers endpoints for user authentication, board management, task assignments, and task commenting.

## Features

- Custom user model using email login
- Token authentication
- Board creation and membership
- Task creation, assignment, and review
- Comment system for tasks
- RESTful API with proper permission handling
- Postman testable endpoints

## Requirements

- Python 3.10+
- Django
- Django REST Framework
- djangorestframework-simplejwt (optional if used)

